{"word":"ἐκφθείρω","slug":"ἐκφθείρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκφθείρω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-φθερῶ</el>) (aor2 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>ἐξέφθαρην</el>) </el><p/><i>to destroy utterly</i><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <el>ἐκφθείρομαι</el>, <i>to be undone, ruined</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: <i>to vanish, pack off</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}